
;1行表示のステータスを切り替える
@CHANGE_TABLE_STATUS

CALL MANYL(5)
PRINTL Change which stats are displayed?
PRINTL ・Name, Condition, and Breast Size are always displayed
CALL HALFLINE
PRINTL [ 0] HP+Screen Options
PRINTL 　　（Schedule or Milk Richness+Milk Production+Lesb）
PRINTL [ 1] HP+Milk Richness+Milk Production
PRINTL [ 2] Spirit Energy Status
PRINTL [ 3] Mana Status
PRINTL [ 4] 身長+種族+ヘアスタイル
PRINTL [ 5] Race+Status or Title
PRINTL [ 6] Job Ability
PRINTL [ 7] 母乳濃度+母乳生産力+陥落状態詳細
PRINTL [ 8] 予定スケジュール+スケジュール（メイン画面のみ、調教対象選択などではHP+母乳）
PRINTL
PRINTL [99] Cancel
INPUT
SIF RESULT >= 0 && RESULT < TABLE_STATUS_PAGE
	FLAG:一覧ステータス切り替え = RESULT





